---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Leadership — Jakub Zientala, Vice President | ARM Management"
  description="Jakub Zientala is Vice President of ARM Management, leading client engagement and the firm's regulatory and market-access work across its international markets."
>
  <main class="ld">
    <section class="ld-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Leadership</span>
        <h1>Jakub Zientala</h1>
        <div class="ld-role">Vice President</div>
        <p class="ld-pos">Leads client engagement and ARM Management's regulatory and market-access proposition across the firm's international markets — advising the senior leadership of international companies, investors and institutions.</p>
        <div class="ld-cta">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request an Introduction →</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn-secondary">Explore Our Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ld-profile">
      <div class="container ld-grid">
        <div class="ld-portrait">
          <div class="ld-frame"><img src="/images/jakub-zientala.jpg" alt="Jakub Zientala, Vice President of ARM Management" width="900" height="1124" /></div>
          <div class="ld-nameplate"><div class="ld-n">Jakub Zientala</div><div class="ld-t">Vice President</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ld-bio">
          <h2>Profile</h2><div class="ld-rule"></div>
          <p class="ld-lede">Jakub Zientala is Vice President of ARM Management, where he leads client engagement and the firm's regulatory and market-access proposition across its international markets. He advises the senior leadership of international companies, investors and institutions — at home in the boardroom, the ministry and the EU institutions alike — helping them enter and operate in markets that are complex, contested, or still being written into law.</p>
          <p>He has built his career at the intersection of European regulation, government affairs and market access — as both strategist and operator. As Director of European and Governmental Affairs for a cross-border industry alliance, he led a multi-year campaign that helped protect an estimated €40 million European market from adverse international regulation, aligning industry leadership, scientific experts and policymakers and carrying the case to UN level. In the same period he advised national authorities on a first-of-its-kind European regulatory framework — work that became a reference point for how emerging sectors are brought into law in Europe.</p>
          <p>He went on to found his own advisory practice, guiding corporates, founders and public institutions on European market entry, regulatory positioning and stakeholder strategy. Earlier, he worked across the European institutional landscape — as a European Climate Pact Ambassador for the European Commission's DG Climate Action, a Youth Delegate of the Netherlands to the Council of Europe, and a research assistant at the European Institute of Public Administration on a Commission-commissioned review of regulatory and legislative processes.</p>
          <p>Equally at ease with a chief executive, a minister or a regulator, Jakub is the adviser senior leaders turn to when an outcome depends on politics and regulation as much as on commercial strategy. He holds a Master's in Public Policy and Human Development from UNU-MERIT / Maastricht University and an LL.B. in European Law from Maastricht University, advises in English, Polish, Czech and Russian, and is based in Brussels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ld-band">
      <div class="container">
        <h3 class="ld-h3">Areas of Focus</h3>
        <div class="ld-focus">
          <span class="ld-chip">Market entry &amp; regulatory strategy</span>
          <span class="ld-chip">Board &amp; C-suite advisory</span>
          <span class="ld-chip">Government relations &amp; public affairs</span>
          <span class="ld-chip">Strategy through to execution</span>
          <span class="ld-chip">Institutional positioning &amp; legitimacy</span>
          <span class="ld-chip">Cross-border stakeholder coalitions</span>
          <span class="ld-chip">Political &amp; regulatory risk</span>
          <span class="ld-chip">Emerging-sector regulation (MiCA / VARA)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ld-cred-wrap">
      <div class="container">
        <h3 class="ld-h3">Credentials &amp; Background</h3>
        <div class="ld-cred">
          <div class="ld-item"><div class="ld-k">Education</div><div class="ld-v">LL.B. European Law — Maastricht University · MA Public Policy — UNU-MERIT / Maastricht</div></div>
          <div class="ld-item"><div class="ld-k">Languages</div><div class="ld-v">English · Polish · Czech · Russian</div></div>
          <div class="ld-item"><div class="ld-k">Focus</div><div class="ld-v">Regulatory strategy · Government affairs · Market access</div></div>
          <div class="ld-item"><div class="ld-k">EU institutions</div><div class="ld-v">European Commission (DG Clima) · EEAS · Council of Europe · Committee of the Regions · EESC · EIPA</div></div>
          <div class="ld-item"><div class="ld-k">Based</div><div class="ld-v">Brussels</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <span class="eyebrow is-center" style="justify-content:center">Private &amp; Confidential</span>
      <h2>Speak with our team directly.</h2>
      <p>Engagements begin with a confidential conversation. ARM Management works with a limited number of clients at a time.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request an Introduction →</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context":"https://schema.org",
    "@type":"Person",
    name:"Jakub Zientala",
    jobTitle:"Vice President",
    worksFor:{ "@type":"Organization", name:"ARM Management", url:"https://arm-management.com" },
    url:"https://arm-management.com/leadership",
    image:"https://arm-management.com/images/jakub-zientala.jpg",
    alumniOf:[
      { "@type":"CollegeOrUniversity", name:"Maastricht University" },
      { "@type":"CollegeOrUniversity", name:"United Nations University (UNU-MERIT)" }
    ],
    knowsLanguage:["English","Polish","Czech","Russian"],
    knowsAbout:["Regulatory strategy","Public affairs","Government relations","Market access","European Union regulation"],
    sameAs:["https://www.linkedin.com/in/jakubzientala"]
  })} />

  <style>
    .ld-hero{background:#0D1B2A;color:#fff;padding:84px 0 72px}
    .ld-hero .eyebrow{color:#C9A227}
    .ld-hero h1{color:#fff;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:300;font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,68px);line-height:1.02;margin:20px 0 10px}
    .ld-role{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,24px);color:#C9A227;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:18px}
    .ld-pos{color:#a9b2bf;max-width:620px;font-size:15px}
    .ld-cta{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:30px}
    .ld-profile{padding:72px 0 30px;background:#F7F3EC}
    .ld-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:340px 1fr;gap:56px;align-items:start}
    .ld-portrait{position:sticky;top:32px}
    .ld-frame{border:1px solid #E2DDD6;padding:10px;background:#FDFAF6}
    .ld-frame img{width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:4px;display:block;box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(13,27,42,.22)}
    .ld-nameplate{margin-top:16px;border-top:2px solid #B8960C;padding-top:12px}
    .ld-nameplate .ld-n{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:24px;color:#0D1B2A;font-weight:600}
    .ld-nameplate .ld-t{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#6B7280;margin-top:3px}
    .ld-bio h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:300;font-size:30px;color:#0D1B2A;margin:0 0 6px}
    .ld-rule{width:48px;height:2px;background:#B8960C;margin:14px 0 22px}
    .ld-bio p{margin-bottom:18px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.65;color:#2C3240}
    .ld-bio .ld-lede{font-size:19px;color:#1d2430}
    .ld-band{background:#FDFAF6;border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-bottom:1px solid #E2DDD6;padding:54px 0}
    .ld-h3{font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#B8960C;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:24px}
    .ld-focus{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}
    .ld-chip{font-size:13.5px;padding:9px 16px;border:1px solid #E2DDD6;border-radius:999px;background:#F7F3EC;color:#2C3240}
    .ld-cred-wrap{padding:54px 0;background:#F7F3EC}
    .ld-cred{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:22px 40px;margin-top:6px}
    .ld-item{border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6;padding-top:12px}
    .ld-k{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:5px}
    .ld-v{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:20px;color:#0D1B2A;line-height:1.3}
    @media(max-width:780px){.ld-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:30px}.ld-portrait{position:static}.ld-cred{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  </style>
</Base>
